---
source: crates/kul-wasm/tests/format.rs
expression: formatted
---
# Cousins and in-laws — one rule, two faces.
#
# When two people marry, the first-listed spouse is the *host* and the
# second *joins* the host's family: the joiner's card moves next to the
# host, and their tie back to their own birth family becomes a connecting
# edge rather than uprooting anyone. This one "absorb rule" handles every
# marriage at every scale. This Rossi family shows its two outcomes side
# by side.
#
#   - Marrying in from outside. Marco marries Elena, who was born into
#     the unrelated Bianchi family. Because the Bianchis aren't otherwise
#     in this tree, Elena's birth family is drawn as a small sub-tree
#     tucked beside the Rossis at the point where she joins.
#
#   - Marrying a cousin. Marco's son Matteo marries Lucia's daughter
#     Giulia — first cousins, both already in this tree. Here the rule has
#     nothing to pull in: Giulia's birth family is already on the canvas,
#     so instead of a new sub-tree her tie is simply drawn as an edge back
#     to her parents, and a faded ghost marks the spot in their children's
#     row that her card left when she moved beside Matteo.
#
# Same rule both times — the only difference is whether the joining
# spouse's family is already present.

# ---- The Rossi grandparents ----
person giuseppe  name:"Giuseppe Rossi"  gender:male    born:1940-05-19
person sofia     name:"Sofia Rossi"     gender:female  born:1943-01-27

marriage m_giuseppe_sofia giuseppe sofia  start:1965-06-12

person marco  name:"Marco Rossi"  gender:male    born:1968-09-30
  birth m_giuseppe_sofia
person lucia  name:"Lucia Rossi"  gender:female  born:1971-04-08
  birth m_giuseppe_sofia

# ---- Marco marries Elena, who joins from the Bianchi family ----
person elena  name:"Elena Bianchi"  gender:female  born:1970-11-15
  birth m_aldo_bianca

marriage m_marco_elena marco elena  start:1995-07-22

person matteo  name:"Matteo Rossi"  gender:male  born:1997-02-14
  birth m_marco_elena

# Elena's birth family — unrelated to the Rossis, so it nests beside them.
person aldo    name:"Aldo Bianchi"    gender:male    born:1942-08-03
person bianca  name:"Bianca Bianchi"  gender:female  born:1945-12-21

marriage m_aldo_bianca aldo bianca  start:1967-05-30

# ---- Lucia marries Paolo ----
person paolo  name:"Paolo Conti"  gender:male  born:1969-03-17

marriage m_lucia_paolo lucia paolo  start:1996-10-05

person giulia  name:"Giulia Conti"  gender:female  born:1998-06-26
  birth m_lucia_paolo

# ---- The cousin marriage: Matteo (Marco's son) and Giulia (Lucia's) ----
# Both are already in this tree, so no new sub-tree is drawn; Giulia's
# birth tie becomes an edge back to m_lucia_paolo.
marriage m_matteo_giulia matteo giulia  start:2020-09-12
